                <h4>Complementary Courses (21 credits)</h4>

    
              <p>Note:<br />
Students must take a minimum of 6 credits at the 400 to 500 level.<br />
Students may not take any courses from their home department(s).</p>
<p>Students complete a minimum of 9 credits each in two areas.</p>
    
      
      
